  <script type="application/json" class="js-product-data" data-id="4642375139388" data-handle="slip-tint-tinted-moisturizer">
    {"id":4642375139388,"title":"Slip Tint Tinted Moisturizer","handle":"slip-tint-tinted-moisturizer","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eSlip into something effortless, award-winning, and multitasking. Slip Tint Tinted Moisturizer sheer shades provide just enough coverage to even your complexion and give you an easy, no-makeup makeup look. Powered by Saie Science, Slip Tint Tinted Moisturizer’s formula is supercharged with clean ingredients like \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eHyaluronic Acid to hydrate, Licorice Root Extract to visibly brighten, and 100% Mineral Non-Nano Zinc Oxide SPF 35 to protect against UVA\/UVB rays and free radical damage. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eEach shade has been crafted to seamlessly blend into a wide range of skin tones and creates that hydrated, Signature SaieGlow™\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eSlip Tint is also dimethicone free, paraben free, talc free, silicone free, synthetic dye free, phthalate free, essential oil free, soy free, natural \u0026amp; synthetic fragrance-free, formulated without gluten \u0026amp; cruelty free. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'San Francisco', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003eGet to know these effective, luxury ingredients:\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e⁃Hyaluronic Acid deeply hydrates\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e⁃Licorice Root extract brightens and refines\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e⁃100% mineral zinc-oxide offers clean SPF protection\u003cbr\u003e⁃Pansy Flower fights free radicals and delivers antioxidants\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"gmail-Apple-converted-space sh-color-black sh-color\"\u003eCheck out our \u003ca href=\"https:\/\/saiehello.com\/pages\/find-your-shade\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eshade finder\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/a\u003e to find your match!\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"p1\"\u003eBest Clean Tinted Moisturizer as part of \u003cstrong data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eAllure Best of Beauty, Cosmopolitan Holy Grail Awards 2021, \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWomen’s Health Beauty Awards,\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNew Beauty Awards, \u003c\/strong\u003eand\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSELF Healthy Beauty Awards\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eCruelty-Free and Formulated without Gluten\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2020-09-16T10:52:00-04:00","created_at":"2020-09-16T10:52:00-04:00","vendor":"Saie","type":"Makeup","tags":["allure","aloe","anti-aging","award-winning","dimethicone-free","dry-skin","dullness","essential oil-free","face","formulated-without-gluten","fragrance-free","hyaluronic acid","hyperpigmentation","jojoba-esters","licorice-root","pansy-flower","Shade Finder","soy-free","spf-","tyb"],"price":3600,"price_min":3600,"price_max":3600,"available":true,"price_varies":false,"compare_at_price":null,"compare_at_price_min":0,"compare_at_price_max":0,"compare_at_price_varies":false,"variants":[{"id":32497603739708,"title":"One: Very Light - Pink","option1":"One: Very Lig