xtra radiant and glowy finish. Active levels of encapsulated Vitamin C help to brighten the appearance of skin and protect against free radicals while Hyaluronic Acid, Vitamin E, and Aloe Vera hydrate and nourish for that signature SaieGlow™.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e"}
