          <div class="details-panel--content-box">
            
              <div class="details-panel--content-wrapper js-ingredient-list-wrapper">
                <div class="details-panel--ingredients-list-wrapper width-40 width-100--med">
  

  <p class="details-panel--ingredient-list js-ingredient-list">
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient active" data-ingredient-info="A safe synthetic mimic of mica. Synthetic mica requires no mining and has no potential for child labor.">Synthetic Fluorphlogopite</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="A mineral found abundantly in sandstone, clay, and granite, as well as in parts of plants. It’s used in this formula to absorb excess oil and set makeup."> Silica</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="Derived fatty alcohol cetearyl alcohol, this ingredient acts as a binder and emollient."> Cetearyl Ethylhexanoate</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="Squalane is a super hydrating ingredient that is derived from olives and carbon neutral sugarcane."> Squalane</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="A synthetic preservative and moisture-binding agent."> 1,2-Hexanediol</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="Derived from caprylic acid, a type of fatty acid that is a natural component of coconut oil, this ingredient acts as humectant and skin conditioning agent. It also functions as a stabilizer and preservative."> Caprylyl Glycol</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="Preservative derived from vegetable glycerin."> Ethylhexylglycerin</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="Plant based stabilizing ingredient."> Gellan Gum</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="Natural mineral."> Mica</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info=" Is used to improve the texture and bind the formula together."> Polysorbate 20</span>
    
      
      <span class="js-ingredient " data-ingredient-info="Derived from natural minerals, our Ecocert iron oxides provide the sparkle and tint.">  +/- May Contain/ Peut Contenir Iron Oxides (CI 7749, CI 77492, CI 77499)</span>
    
  </p>
</div><!--
--><div class="details-panel--ingredients-info-wrapper width-60 width-100--med">
  <p class="details-panel--ingredient-info text-large-body js-ingredient-info"> A safe synthetic mimic of mica. Synthetic mica requires no mining and has no potential for child labor.</p>
</div>

              </div>
            
