<ol><li>Twist open the sifter and tap some product into the cap.</li><li>Swirl the Fluffy Brush or your favorite powder brush in the cap, working the powder into the bristles so it’s evenly distributed.</li><li>For pinpointed application on high-shine zones use tapered tip. For a radiantly diffused look all over the face bounce and roll the fluffy edges of the brush along the skin.</li></ol>


